Puppet module: subversion

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages subversion
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include subversion              # Install and run subversion with standard configurations.
include subversion::disable     # Disable subversion service.
include subversion::disableboot # Disable subversion service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include subversion::absent      # Remove subversion package.

DEPENDENCIES:
common::untar-gz 
